Endmembers from Alkire and Trefrey 2006

\(SIM+MW+PML = 1\)

\(5*SIM + 0*MW + 32.1*PML = S\)

\(-2*SIM + x*MW + -3.5*PML = O\)

where \(x\) is the value for meltwater of rivers associated with a particular lagoon
